('19782ca7-1972-4e86-b26a-a329460ff850','Butternut Squash','Complex Carb','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Feed cooked and plain; avoid seasoned preparations.', 'Provides fiber, beta-carotene, potassium, and digestible carbohydrate.', 'Useful as a lower-fat carbohydrate and fiber source in homemade diets.'),
('c9ff1aa1-87cc-4554-9dd7-62a27fa8cd87','Zucchini','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Feed plain and cooked or finely chopped; low calorie but not nutrient-dense enough to displace major ingredients.', 'Low-calorie vegetable with potassium, vitamin C, and modest fiber.', 'Used to add bulk and moisture to weight-control recipes.'),
('99bd6edb-b0f8-4b13-85b7-e4ef4c1bc0bd','Carrots','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Cooking improves digestibility for some pets; feed plain and chopped.', 'Provide beta-carotene, fiber, potassium, and low fat.', 'Often used as a low-calorie vegetable inclusion or treat in homemade feeding.'),
('fd537a47-9b29-44fe-8cc7-4bf0e70a1b72','Green Beans','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Serve plain with no salt; canned salted products are inappropriate.', 'Contain fiber, manganese, vitamin K, and low calories.', 'Useful for satiety support and low-calorie bulk in weight-control diets.'),
('1cf58821-fcdb-4879-96ed-c4a1293d2ea8','Broccoli','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Feed small cooked portions; large amounts may cause GI upset.', 'Contains fiber, vitamin C, folate, and phytonutrients.', 'Can be used as a low-calorie vegetable adjunct in modest quantities.'),
('4dfc5d27-d9e5-43d5-8d6f-f6f27827509e','Cauliflower','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Introduce gradually due to gas potential.', 'Low-calorie vegetable with fiber and vitamin C.', 'Used to add bulk and texture diversity in homemade diets.'),
('f7dc17ad-aebf-46ff-a523-8d9c40206d08','Celery','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Cut finely to reduce choking risk; avoid salty additions.', 'Low-calorie vegetable with fiber and potassium.', 'Mainly used for low-energy bulk rather than nutrient density.'),
('9908f2df-151d-4ced-b740-721b605ced5e','Cucumber','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Serve plain and sliced; low nutrient density means it should remain a minor inclusion.', 'Very high moisture, low calorie, modest potassium.', 'Helpful for hydration support and low-calorie treat use.'),
('581be28c-3a06-49d2-bab0-c61ab73d4e82','Cabbage','Vegetable','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Use small cooked amounts to limit GI gas or irritation.', 'Contains fiber, vitamin C, and some vitamin K.', 'Included occasionally for low-calorie vegetable variety.'),
('9effa987-f2b3-42d0-ab98-68f9e1c8bde3','Spinach','Vegetable','{"DOG"}', 'Use sparingly; oxalates may be undesirable in calcium oxalate stone-prone patients.', 'Provides folate, iron, vitamin K, magnesium, and carotenoids.', 'Used in small quantities for micronutrient enrichment, not as a major ingredient.'),
