('04f36d61-8e15-4114-bf3d-b0e7d6236baa','Swiss Chard','Vegetable','{"DOG"}', 'Use sparingly where oxalate issues are a concern.', 'Provides magnesium, potassium, vitamin K, and carotenoids.', 'Can broaden micronutrient diversity in dog diets when used conservatively.'),
('947e4456-2c8c-4d60-8d95-59e49606de4d','Beet Pulp','Soluble Fiber','{"DOG"}', 'Fiber sources should be introduced gradually and balanced against stool quality.', 'Moderately fermentable fiber used to support colonic health and stool formation.', 'Useful in canine recipes needing stool quality support without excessive bulk.'),
