('f3f182f5-d176-4975-a33b-0cb95889f8a9','Parsley','Supplement','{"DOG"}', 'Use as a garnish-level herb only; not a major ingredient.', 'Contains vitamin K, vitamin C, and plant phytonutrients.', 'Used in tiny amounts for flavor and herb diversity.'),
('0454dd69-df3d-48cf-bb38-bf4f80d66d56','Basil','Supplement','{"DOG"}', 'Use sparingly and plain.', 'Contains plant antioxidants and aroma compounds with minimal caloric load.', 'Sometimes used in gourmet homemade canine recipes for flavor variety.'),
('77f5f643-a4be-4285-bd9c-a8407b76d8bc','Rosemary','Supplement','{"DOG"}', 'Use very small culinary amounts only.', 'Provides aromatic phytochemicals and negligible macronutrients.', 'Used primarily for flavoring in extremely low inclusion amounts.'),
('8cfc2f2b-a6cc-4b4a-bc38-6d90dc8b173b','Ginger','Supplement','{"DOG"}', 'Use small amounts only; excess may irritate the GI tract.', 'Contains gingerols and minimal calories in culinary doses.', 'Sometimes used in dog formulations aimed at nausea-sensitive patients under supervision.'),
('46976281-a839-49af-bf70-aa0a4f8ccc1a','Turmeric','Supplement','{"DOG"}', 'Use cautiously and not as a replacement for medical therapy; bioavailability is variable.', 'Contains curcuminoids with minimal protein/fat contribution in culinary doses.', 'Included in some anti-inflammatory canine feeding approaches in very small quantities.'),
('7ec6c576-9cea-4388-b165-11de96436eb2','Kelp Powder','Supplement','{"DOG","CAT"}', 'Use carefully due to iodine concentration; excess can disrupt thyroid balance.', 'Iodine-rich marine supplement sometimes containing trace minerals.', 'Used to supply iodine in homemade diets when formulation calculations indicate need.'),
